Dialogue: 2,0:20:14.35,0:20:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3\an7\i1\b1\fnComic Sans MS\blur3\fad(0,300)}Sekarang aku lupakannya sebagai tubuh ku{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:20:21.74,0:20:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\an7\i1\b1\fnComic Sans MS\blur3\fad(0,300)}Ima wa Subete wo Wasure yo{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:20:21.74,0:20:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3\an7\i1\b1\fnComic Sans MS\blur3\fad(0,300)}yang telah diambil oleh kegelapan keji{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:20:27.45,0:20:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\an7\i1\b1\fnComic Sans MS\blur3\fad(0,300)}Hageshii Koe ga Kokoro wo \NIyashite Yami wo Tatsukara{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:20:27.45,0:20:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3\an7\i1\b1\fnComic Sans MS\blur3\fad(0,300)}Suara bernyala mu melawan \Nkegelapan dan mengubati hati ku{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:20:41.44,0:20:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\an7\i1\b1\fnComic Sans MS\blur3\fad(0,300)}Hikari no Naka Dakarete Nemuru{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:20:41.44,0:20:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3\an7\i1\b1\fnComic Sans MS\blur3\fad(0,300)}Wajah mu seperti malaikat{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:20:47.67,0:20:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\an7\i1\b1\fnComic Sans MS\blur3\fad(0,300)}Tenshi no Youna Yokogao ni{\b0\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:20:47.67,0:20:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3\an7\i1\b1\fnComic Sans MS\blur3\fad(0,300)}yang sedang tidur selesa di bawah cahaya{\b0\i0}
